  "title": "Creamy Mediterranean Tahini Stir-fry",
  "description": "A sweet, silky keto-friendly dish featuring grilled vegetables with a creamy tahini sauce that's perfect for weeknight dinners.",
  "cuisine": "Mediterranean",
